data.description: Welcome to your new home! Wonderfully located in SW Cape Coral, this 3/2 Florida Ranch Style single family home is in a great central neighborhood, on a quiet street and not far from great shopping, dining and entertainment. This home  features a brand NEW roof along with city water/sewer , Assessments are IN and PAID.  NO HOA dues. NOT in a flood zone! No flooding during Hurricane Ian. The garage has been partially enclosed giving room to a 4th bedroom all while maintaining storage area along with an inside laundry room! Don't miss out on this opportunity, schedule your showing today! MOTIVATED SELLERS!
